perspective correction (do after vehicle tracking):
see PERSPECTIVE_CORRECTION.md

  - correct angled/skewed plate crops before OCR using homography
  - Option A (recommended): swap to a keypoint YOLO model that returns 4 plate corners
  - Option B: contour detection on the crop to find the plate quadrilateral
  - add --perspective CLI flag (off by default)
  - only worth prioritising if camera is steep-angle and angled plates are the main OCR failure mode

